<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>University Website</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/mainstyle.css">

    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@fortawesome/fontawesome-free@6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
    <section class="header">
        <nav>
            <a href="/">
                <img src="images/logo.png" alt="University Logo">
            </a>
            <div class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
                <i class="fa fa-times" onclick="hideMenu()"></i>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="/">HOME</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/about">ABOUT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/courses">COURSES</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/blog">BLOG</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/contact">CONTACT</a></li>
                    <li><a href="/logout">LOGOUT</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <i class="fa fa-bars" onclick="showMenu()"></i>
        </nav>
        
        <div class="text-box">
            <h1>World's Best University</h1>
            <p>Welcome to our prestigious university, where excellence meets innovation. Our institution is dedicated to providing top-tier education and fostering a community of forward-thinking leaders. Making a website is now one of the easiest things in the world. You just need to learn HTML, CSS, JavaScript and you are good to go.</p>
            <a href="#" class="hero-btn">Visit Us To Know More</a>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="course">
        <h1>Courses We Offer</h1>
        <p>Explore our diverse range of courses designed to help you achieve your academic and career goals.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="course-col">
                <h3>Intermediate</h3>
                <p>Our intermediate courses provide a strong foundation in various subjects, preparing you for advanced studies and future academic challenges.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-col">
                <h3>Degree</h3>
                <p>Pursue your bachelor's degree in a variety of fields, with programs designed to equip you with the knowledge and skills needed for a successful career.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="course-col">
                <h3>Post Graduate</h3>
                <p>Advance your education with our postgraduate programs, offering specialized knowledge and research opportunities in your chosen field.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="campus">
        <h1>Our Global Campuses</h1>
        <p>Join our global community and gain access to our campuses around the world, providing unique cultural and educational experiences.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="campus-col">
                <img src="images/london.png" alt="London Campus">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>LONDON</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="campus-col">
                <img src="images/newyork.png" alt="New York Campus">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>NEW YORK</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="campus-col">
                <img src="images/washington.png" alt="Washington Campus">
                <div class="layer">
                    <h3>WASHINGTON</h3>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="facilities">
        <h1>Our Facilities</h1>
        <p>Explore our state-of-the-art facilities designed to enhance your learning experience and support your academic journey. Whether you're conducting research in our advanced laboratories, collaborating with peers in our modern classrooms, or relaxing in our student lounges, we provide the resources you need to succeed.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="facilities-col">
                <img src="images/library.png" alt="Library">
                <h3>World Class Library</h3>
                <p>Our world-class library is equipped with extensive collections of books, journals, and digital resources to support your academic research and learning. Whether you're exploring rare manuscripts or accessing the latest scholarly publications, our library provides a serene and conducive environment for study and intellectual growth.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="facilities-col">
                <img src="images/basketball.png" alt="Basketball Playground">
                <h3>Largest Playground</h3>
                <p>Enjoy our expansive playground facilities, perfect for recreational activities and sports events. With state-of-the-art equipment and spacious grounds, our playground fosters a vibrant atmosphere where students can engage in physical fitness and teamwork.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="facilities-col">
                <img src="images/cafeteria.png" alt="Cafeteria">
                <h3>Tasty and Healthy Food</h3>
                <p>Indulge in delicious and nutritious meals at our cafeteria. From fresh salads to hearty entrees, our dining options cater to diverse tastes and dietary preferences, ensuring a satisfying culinary experience for all students and staff.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonials">
        <h1>What Our Students Say</h1>
        <p>Discover what our students have to say about their experiences at our university.</p>
        <div class="row">
            <div class="testimonial-col">
                <img src="images/user1.jpg" alt="Student 1">
                <div>
                    <p>"The faculty and resources at this university are truly exceptional. I've gained invaluable knowledge and skills that have prepared me for my career."</p>
                    <h3>John Doe</h3>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star-half-o"></i>
                    </div>
                    <i>Computer Science Student</i>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="testimonial-col">
                <img src="images/user2.jpg" alt="Student 2">
                <div>
                    <p>"I'm grateful for the supportive community and the opportunities I've had here. It's been a transformative experience both academically and personally."</p>
                    <h3>Jane Smith</h3>
                    <div class="rating">
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                        <i class="fa fa-star"></i>
                    </div>
                    <i>Business Administration Student</i>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta">
        <h1>Enroll For Our Various Online Courses <br>Anywhere From 
            The World</h1>
        <a href="" class="hero-btn">CONTACT US</a>
    </section>

    <section class="footer">
        <h4>About Us</h4>
        <p>Welcome to our college, where excellence meets opportunity.<br>We are committed to providing our students with a transformative educational <br>experience that prepares them for success in their careers and beyond. 
            With state-of-the-art facilities, <br>
            dedicated faculty, and a vibrant community,
             we strive to foster a supportive environment that encourages intellectual curiosity, creativity, and personal growth.</p>

        <div class="icons">
            <i class="fab fa-facebook"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-instagram"></i>
            <i class="fab fa-linkedin"></i>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- JavaScript for Toggle Menu -->
    <script>
        var navLinks = document.getElementById("navLinks");

        function showMenu() {
            navLinks.style.right = "0";
        }

        function hideMenu() {
            navLinks.style.right = "-200px";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
